    <!-- Terms of use -->
    <string name="terms_title">Terms of use</string>
    <string name="terms_effective">AutoGuard %1$s</string>
    <string name="terms_body">AutoGuard automates turning the official WireGuard app\'s VPN tunnel on and off based on the Wi-Fi network you are connected to. AutoGuard is not a VPN, does not route or inspect your network traffic, and keeps no personal data off your device.\n\nNo warranty. AutoGuard is provided \"as is\" and \"as available\", without warranty of any kind to the maximum extent permitted by law. It is not guaranteed to be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, and cannot guarantee the tunnel is active at any given moment - protection depends on the WireGuard app, Android, and your device.\n\nNot affiliated. AutoGuard is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to WireGuard or its trademark owner.\n\nYour responsibility. You are responsible for your VPN configuration and credentials, choosing which networks to trust, granting the permissions AutoGuard needs, and complying with all applicable laws.\n\nNo liability. To the maximum extent permitted by law, the developer is not liable for any data loss, security incident, exposure resulting from a tunnel failing to start, or any direct or indirect damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, the app.\n\nBy using AutoGuard you accept these terms.</string>
